                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9798" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1471</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">703 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">酒香飘沙洲：沙洲优黄文化园的品牌魅力辐射</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wine Aroma Wafts Over Shazhou: The Radiating Brand Charm of Shazhou Youhuang Cultural Park</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨帆，陈静一，张正勇，孟秀丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏张家港酿酒有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏张家港酿酒有限公司；沙洲优黄；沙洲优黄文化园；工业旅游；品牌传播；产业融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhangjiagang Brewery; Shazhou Youhuang; Shazhou Youhuang Cultural Park; Industrial Tourism; Brand Communication; Industrial Integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在文旅融合与产业升级的国家战略推动下，工业旅游已成为企业实现品牌增值与文化传播的重要路径。江苏张家港酿酒有限公司始终坚持“传播黄酒文化，推动产业发展”的理念，在保证产品质量与文化传承的同时，大力发展工业旅游，设计并建造了沙洲优黄文化园，开展品牌传播，注重文化保护，积极举办各类文化交流活动，有效提升了品牌知名度。本案例通过描写沙洲优黄开展工业旅游的具体实践，旨在使学生掌握工业旅游的内涵、模式与优势，品牌传播、产业融合理论，使学生了解企业开展工业旅游、品牌传播的条件、模式，启发学生思考品牌传播、产业融合对于企业发展的作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Driven by the national strategy of integrating culture and tourism and industrial upgrading, industrial tourism has become an important path for enterprises to realize brand value enhancement and cultural dissemination. Zhangjiagang Brewery has always adhered to the philosophy of “Disseminating Huangjiu Culture and Promoting Industrial Development”. While ensuring product quality and cultural inheritance, the company has vigorously developed industrial tourism by designing and constructing the Shazhou Youhuang Cultural Park, carrying out brand communication, emphasizing cultural preservation, and actively organizing various cultural exchange activities, thereby effectively enhancing brand awareness. This case study, through depicting the specific practices of industrial tourism at Shazhou Youhuang, aims to enable students to grasp the essence, models, and advantages of industrial tourism, as well as theories of brand communication and industrial integration. It also informs students about the conditions and models for enterprises to engage in industrial tourism and brand communication, inspiring them to reflect on the role of brand communication and industrial integration in corporate development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销学》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工业旅游；品牌传播；产业融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
